OL,3,C'Be gentle': Liam Payne's girlfriend
OL,4,Cshares post about grief on Christmas
OL,6,FLiam Payne's girlfriend Kate Cassidy
OL,7,Fhas shared a message about
OL,8,Fexperiencing sadness and grief during
OL,9,Fthe holiday season following the
OL,10,Fsinger's death.
OL,12,FOne Direction star Payne died aged 31
OL,13,Fon October 16 after falling from the
OL,14,Fthird-floor balcony of a hotel in the
OL,15,FArgentine capital Buenos Aires.
OL,17,FIn an Instagram Story post on
OL,18,FWednesday, Cassidy advised others to
OL,19,F"be gentle" with those around them
OL,20,Fduring the Christmas period and sent
OL,21,Fher love to those "carrying grief".
