OL,6,FThe message read: "As the holidays are
OL,7,Fhere, I realise it is a time for
OL,8,Fhappiness and joy, but it is also a
OL,9,Ftime of sadness and grief for so many.
OL,11,F"Be gentle with those around you this
OL,12,Ftime of year, as the holidays can feel
OL,13,Fdifferent for everyone."
