OL,6,FIt continued: "Sending all my love to
OL,7,Fthose carrying grief this holiday. I
OL,8,Fhope the seasons bring you comfort and
OL,9,Fpeace."
OL,11,F"Wishing everyone a love-filled and
OL,12,Fhealthy holiday season this year."
OL,14,FCassidy joined Payne's family and One
OL,15,FDirection bandmates last month at a
OL,16,Fprivate funeral in Buckinghamshire.
OL,18,FShe said her heart was "shattered" and
OL,19,Fthat she had "lost the best part of
OL,20,Fmyself" in an emotional tribute.
