OL,6,F"Liam, I know we'll be together
OL,7,Fforever, but not in the way we had
OL,8,Fplanned", she added.
OL,10,F"You'll always be with me. I've gained
OL,11,Fa guardian angel. I will love you for
OL,12,Fthe rest of my life and beyond,
OL,13,Fcarrying our dreams and memories with
OL,14,Fme everywhere I go."
OL,16,FPayne, who rose to fame with boy band
OL,17,FOne Direction when they were formed on
OL,18,FITV talent show The X Factor in 2010,
OL,19,Fdied of multiple traumas and "internal
OL,20,Fand external haemorrhage", a post-
OL,21,Fmortem examination report said.
